Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.90,0:00:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.08,0:00:19.91,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdays 開始的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.98,0:00:22.92,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,給世界一個吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.39,0:00:25.98,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing in thewind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.05,0:00:32.15,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,把一點點的勇氣和愛放進口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.66,0:00:40.33,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish如果我有翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.04,0:00:50.10,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管悲傷、過去還是不安 都能夠飛越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.18,0:00:52.24,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,OhYeah！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.31,0:00:56.58,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.05,0:01:01.04,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemyway！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.12,0:01:03.95,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想用這掌心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.02,0:01:07.76,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.23,0:01:17.00,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,朝向無盡的天空和大地 以及未來旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.07,0:01:20.27,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,剛長出的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.34,0:01:23.47,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh！ 一定一定一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.54,0:01:24.64,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.71,0:01:28.41,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,展現光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.45,0:01:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點唐突\N不過我希望妳能協助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.62,0:01:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協助？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.33,0:01:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.66,0:01:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你們在一起的那個少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.83,0:01:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.00,0:01:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音她怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.24,0:01:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺了那個少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.68,0:02:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#08 羈絆與祈禱的小夜曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.98,0:02:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看一下帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.09,0:02:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.86,0:02:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要還待在這裡\N她應該不會有事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.49,0:02:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.80,0:02:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.97,0:02:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.38,0:02:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己會不會覺得很奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.28,0:02:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你特別寵詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.59,0:02:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也是一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.09,0:02:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子會不會是異能者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帶她回來這件事也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.30,0:02:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假設是這孩子用了某種能力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能，妳想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.54,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.28,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...妳在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.61,0:03:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的哥哥和姊姊幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才向妳尋求協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要殺那麼小的孩子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂妳的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.13,0:03:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法對她下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點殺了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.47,0:03:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非得做這種事不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.58,0:03:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則，妳的哥哥和姊姊都會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是秩序守護者的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳做的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說說話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.08,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的哥哥和姊姊都會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音，妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.34,0:04:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.61,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向詩音道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.42,0:04:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非道歉不可？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音比我還重要嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.99,0:05:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知不知道妳對詩音做了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不相信我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還說什麼要保護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.33,0:05:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在對自己有好處的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說些漂亮話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耍耍帥罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.57,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人都可以是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能施捨同情心\N讓你沉浸在優越感當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.64,0:05:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算對象不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也能得到滿足，對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.41,0:05:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳是這樣看我的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太遺憾了，公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.61,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是稀奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個竟然會\N吵完了架以後還賭氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.73,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要好好談談才可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別在這種時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏儂也跟妳一樣\N不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒，過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.87,0:06:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去鎮上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把馬車賣掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，夏儂哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.01,0:06:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要擅自決定\N那麼重要的事情...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.41,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經決定好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.54,0:06:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經別無選擇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，德拉克諾夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂、拉蔻兒和帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音都喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂和帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在感情不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.48,0:07:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...偶爾會這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是詩音的錯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是詩音的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是大家都有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.33,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音我問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.93,0:07:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音想一直待在我們身邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.60,0:08:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在我們身邊說不定會死喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.24,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣也沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音不會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，我是說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.51,0:08:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.45,0:08:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也許要花點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想帕希菲卡應該會了解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正她就是那樣的丫頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.86,0:08:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的每一個首飾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都有著不同的意義與祈願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的眼光真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.74,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我最喜歡的一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.21,0:09:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算便宜一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，好貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.19,0:09:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡...花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂！夏儂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.62,0:09:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還喲什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的傷勢是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音，我問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不說話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥竟然會受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正常來說根本是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.65,0:10:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為有妳在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.82,0:10:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.27,0:10:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給帕希菲卡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然想用這種東西跟我和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.01,0:10:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一點創意都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.96,0:11:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.83,0:11:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是詩音為妳選的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.23,0:11:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說裡面含有羈絆的祈願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱能永遠在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.37,0:11:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱就算分離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.67,0:11:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能夠再次相聚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.82,0:11:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒在一起嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近沒有她的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.52,0:12:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還問去哪裡，當然是去找她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.49,0:12:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.03,0:12:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為像拉蔻兒姊一樣的姊姊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.17,0:12:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.04,0:12:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在哪裡？詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.45,0:12:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是飛來橫禍啊，我的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也遇到一些麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然曾經試著來過這邊一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻遇到了阻礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻礙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個少女\N不離開你一定距離的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我連跟你說話都辦不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道詩音的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個少女本名叫夕紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.61,0:13:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是重武裝砲兵型的秩序守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音，妳在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，給我等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓到妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算抓到妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.95,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有必要離開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使維持現在這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.02,0:13:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的人生就已經夠複雜的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.79,0:13:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就算多了一個怪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也差不了多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.53,0:14:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後要好好地叫我姊姊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.94,0:14:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.55,0:14:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們說好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.83,0:14:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，不要哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，回家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思打擾你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳把那孩子還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.18,0:14:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是秩序守護者\N史黛雅希比里昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秩序守護者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類無法違抗秩序守護者的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.22,0:14:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的例外是帕希菲卡．卡蘇魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.29,0:14:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，現在除非在\N極度恐懼或憤怒的狀態下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則，這個特性不會顯現出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.13,0:15:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們到現在都沒辦法違抗\N夕紫的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.17,0:15:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果夕紫覺醒恢復原來的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概已經當場殺了你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，在她所依附的軀體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還殘存人類的屬性之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法對她下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.35,0:15:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我曾向帕希菲卡．卡蘇魯提議\N要她殺掉夕紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，她似乎不願意接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個實在太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音才不是那種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.93,0:15:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這種感情也是\N夕紫操縱下的產物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，這是我自己的意志...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.91,0:15:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的主人，有話以後再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像又有一台秩序守護者來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在夕紫和你妹妹那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我真的嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到她會被你們撿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.46,0:16:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子可是我們的同伴喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就告訴妳好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.50,0:16:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秩序守護者是兩人一組的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.13,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平時因為重武裝砲兵型力量太大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不方便使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.74,0:16:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以都以壓縮狀態\N保存在異相空間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了對抗上次那個賽菲莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因而啟動了解壓縮作業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.08,0:16:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...妳在說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.15,0:16:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是跟那孩子一組的葛里爾\N卻搶先行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.39,0:16:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果一下子就被你們解決掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在解壓縮之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.36,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連上下左右都搞不清楚\N就被放了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.60,0:16:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得已我只好\N代替葛里爾出來找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來吧，夕紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.70,0:16:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩可是妳的敵人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.81,0:16:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...妳不要亂講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳罵我亂講...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音，快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.52,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢復妳應有的模樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.56,0:17:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒的感覺如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.92,0:17:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夕紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.86,0:17:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是史黛雅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說我的另一半...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛里爾死了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，很遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.94,0:17:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.87,0:18:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.24,0:18:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.71,0:18:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.55,0:18:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，詩音到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.55,0:18:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如妳所看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是我們的敵人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不承認這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的主人，借你的身體一用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.18,0:18:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲莉絲已經跟龍騎士\N合為一體了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.79,0:18:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過看來還沒有完全復活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與龍騎士的精神統一狀態\N也還有誤差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.79,0:18:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.66,0:18:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛解壓縮完還沒做微調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.03,0:19:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太勉強的話有可能會引發核分裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要我動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.90,0:19:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.41,0:19:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過也有可能\N把妳捲進去一起陪葬喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要試試看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.45,0:19:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.69,0:19:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們不打算跟妳戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，夕紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.76,0:19:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.43,0:19:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會毀了妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據賽菲莉絲的說法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夕紫心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.68,0:20:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還留有詩音人格的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎是零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.45,0:20:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且她說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見面的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概真的會拼個你死我活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.26,0:20:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能恢復原來的模樣了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為多了一個妹妹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.40,0:20:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想說可以擺個姊姊的架子之類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定那種感覺還不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.34,0:20:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能這樣想的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.27,0:21:18.14,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,滋潤大地的雨水靜靜地飄下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.30,0:21:23.54,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,落在很遠很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.61,0:21:30.91,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,將這愛的雨滴獻給 某個等待已久的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.98,0:21:36.51,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,清晨的微風吹過沾有雨滴的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.59,0:21:41.05,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你感覺到什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.53,0:21:44.96,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,這雨滴有著明白的含意 比一切都還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.03,0:21:49.47,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那唯一的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.94,0:21:56.34,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,停駐在追趕著的雲影下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.41,0:22:00.00,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,在這心靈的旅程中想要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.08,0:22:03.05,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡不管到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.12,0:22:09.58,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天會再聽到熟悉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.66,0:22:16.46,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,船將會啟航啟航 船會航行到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.53,0:22:21.90,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯要相信廣闊的世界 到未知的海洋的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.97,0:22:28.64,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,你要前往遠方然後奔向未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.14,0:22:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走在積雪道路上的\N帕希菲卡一行人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.18,0:22:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然發現了\N用魔法隱藏起來的村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.92,0:22:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是從村子裡出來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.32,0:22:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不太歡迎他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.85,0:22:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道他們厭惡人類嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.75,0:22:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主下一回\N「獻給異教徒的安魂曲」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.73,0:22:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待